				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-fc33d65 elementor-nav-menu__align-left elementor-nav-menu--dropdown-none elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-tablet__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-nav-menu" data-id="fc33d65" data-element_type="widget" data-settings="{&quot;layout&quot;:&quot;vertical&quot;,&quot;submenu_icon&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;&lt;i class=\&quot;fas fa-caret-down\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/i&gt;&quot;,&quot;library&quot;:&quot;fa-solid&quot;}}" data-widget_type="nav-menu.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
						<nav class="elementor-nav-menu--main elementor-nav-menu__container elementor-nav-menu--layout-vertical e--pointer-underline e--animation-fade">
				<ul id="menu-1-fc33d65" class="elementor-nav-menu sm-vertical"><li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-post menu-item-15619"><a href="https://stroybrigada-365.ru/otmostki/" class="elementor-item">Отмостки</a></li>
<li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-post menu-item-15617"><a href="https://stroybrigada-365.ru/montazh-krovli-i-stropil/" class="elementor-item">Монтаж кровли и стропил</a></li>
<li class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-post menu-item-15621"><a href="https://stroybrigada-365.ru/stroitelstvo-pristroek/" class="elementor-item">Строительство пристроек</a></li>
